Definition:
------------
 You can easily customize the network configuration for you amazon virtual private cloud
 For example you can create public facing subnet for your webervers that access to the internet
 and place your backend systems such as db in private facing subnet with no internet acess.
 You can leverage multiple layers of security inclduing SG,NACL

Traffic -> Internet Gateway --> Router ---> Route Table ---> NACL --> Security Group ---> EC2
                  (or)
           Virtual Private Gateway

